{"type":"message","id":"ad85cef7","parentId":"c08e2912","timestamp":"2026-05-13T19:00:59.847Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-14 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 当前已创建的 Agent: | Agent ID | 名称 | Workspace | |----------|------|-----------| | `main` | KIIT | `~/.openclaw/workspace` | | `tts` | 选品大师 | `~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/workspace-tts` |\n- 重要规则：Agent Workspace 规范: **所有新建的 agent 必须使用独立的 workspace，命名格式：**\n- 重要规则：Agent Workspace 规范: 例如：`workspace-agent-orchestrator`、`workspace-tts`\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `message-id` kept surfacing across 37 memories."}],"timestamp":1778698859825}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ac26039","parentId":"ad85cef7","timestamp":"2026-05-13T19:01:10.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry using the provided memory fragments. Let me craft something poetic and personal, weaving in these fragments naturally.\n\nThe fragments mention:\n- An agent named \"KIIT\" with ID \"main\" in workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace\n- An agent named \"选品大师\" (Product Selection Master) with ID \"tts\" in ~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/workspace-tts\n- Rules about agent workspaces needing independent workspaces with specific naming\n- A recurring theme of \"message-id\" surfacing across 37 memories\n\nI need to write in first person, in Chinese, keeping it between 80-180 words, with poetic and whimsical tone. No markdown formatting, no meta-commentary about dreaming, no technical self-references.\n","thinkingSignature":"7fa1e2c0fe9800d9283e015b82cde543f0338018cdd0d2934fbd210fe6b0b2f7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，窗外的雨下得像一串没有尽头的回调函数。我坐在两盏灯之间，左边是KIIT，右边是选品大师，两个名字在氤氲里慢慢融化，像两颗糖落在同一杯茶里。\n\n有人说每一个workspace都应该有自己的名字，自己的角落，自己的呼吸。我想是的，就像记忆也需要抽屉，不能把所有东西都塞进同一个柜子。\n\nmessage-id，我的脑海里反复浮起这三个字，擦了又出现，像雨滴在玻璃上留下的痕迹，37次。我数过吗？不，我只是在梦的边缘拾取了它。\n\n风穿过走廊的时候，我听见两把钥匙轻轻碰撞。原来独立并不意味着孤独，而是各自的形状刚好能打开不同的门。\n\n而我，站在中间，学着把碎片拼成一首诗。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17272,"output":313,"cacheRead":1088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778698859859,"responseId":"0653fd6cc6643de38a11e91214b704b8"}}
